 <p>
 <anchor type="textConst" xml:id="TG76"/>Das was Sie<note type="textConst" xml:id="TG76h">quer am rechten Rand</note> über’n <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="KL201-1"/>
 <rs type="work" ref="#pmb32332" subtype="implied">Automobil</rs>
 <note type="commentary" xml:id="KL201-1h">In <rs ref="#pmb32332" type="work">Entgegen</rs> (<bibl>
 <rs ref="#pmb29414" type="org">Neues Wiener Tagblatt</rs>,
 Jg. 36, Nr. 179, <date>1. 7. 1902</date>,
 S. 1–2</bibl>) schildert <rs ref="#pmb10815" type="person">Bahr</rs> ein
 Automobilrennen.</note> geſchrieben haben, war <hi rend="underline" n="1">ſehr</hi> gut.</p>
 <p>
 <date>3 VII 02</date>.</p>
 <closer>Viele Grüße<space unit="chars" quantity="3"/>
 <signed>Hugo</signed>
 </closer>
 </div>
 <div type="writingSession" n="2">
 <p>
 <handShift scribe="#2121"/>
 <anchor type="textConst" xml:id="TG77"/>Ich auch<note type="textConst" xml:id="TG77h">am rechten Rand auf dem Kopf</note>
 </p>
 <closer>
 <signed>Arthur.</signed>
 </closer>

